{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778899815851,"sessionID":"ses_1d1560b64ffene3xA8b0eZNPB1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:50","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","content":"Hi @raymond91125,\n\nI have reviewed and validated the changes for this issue. Both the new term **GO:7770062 vesicle membrane tethering activity** and the extended definition of **GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity** (to include \"vesicle\") were already present in the branch. \n\nIn addition, I added the missing `term_tracker_item` link on **GO:0140177** pointing back to issue #31863, so the definition extension is properly tracked.\n\nValidation performed:\n- SPARQL QC: 0 violations\n- ELK reasoning: no errors\n- PMID references verified (19887069 and 19575650)\n\nChanges committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nLet me know if anything further is needed.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778899815846,"end":1778899815850}},"id":"prt_e2eb1083b001GvTtC2JZfKNosX","sessionID":"ses_1d1560b64ffene3xA8b0eZNPB1","messageID":"msg_e2eb0fb3b001Z4nfGTxs8OJ3H2"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778899821007,"sessionID":"ses_1d1560b64ffene3xA8b0eZNPB1","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:51","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","content":"## Summary\n\nThis PR addresses issue #31863: NTR for \"vesicle membrane tethering activity\" and extension of GO:0140177 definition.\n\n### Changes Made\n\nThe ontology already contained the main changes from a prior curation pass. This PR adds one missing metadata item:\n\n- **GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity** — added `property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31863\" xsd:anyURI` to track the definition extension requested in this issue.\n\n### Verification of Existing Changes\n\nI independently validated the pre-existing edits (new term GO:7770062 and updated GO:0140177 definition):\n\n- **GO:7770062 vesicle membrane tethering activity**\n  - Correctly placed as `is_a: GO:0140177 ! membrane-membrane adaptor activity`\n  - Definition: \"A membrane-membrane adaptor activity that provides the first point of contact and physically bridges the vesicle membrane and its target membrane prior to vesicle docking and fusion.\"\n  - References: PMID:19887069 (Sztul & Lupashin 2009, ER-Golgi tethering) and PMID:19575650 (Yu & Hughson 2010, general review of tethering factors)\n  - Synonyms: \"vesicle membrane tether activity\" (EXACT), \"vesicle tethering activity\" (EXACT)\n  - Namespace: molecular_function\n  - term_tracker_item points to issue #31863\n  - Metadata: created_by dragon-ai-agent, creation_date 2026-04-13T23:43:55Z\n\n- **GO:0140177 membrane-membrane adaptor activity**\n  - Definition correctly extended to: \"The binding activity of a molecule that brings together two membranes, either via membrane lipid binding or by interacting with a membrane protein, to establish or maintain the localization of the protein, protein complex, vesicle or organelle.\"\n\n### Validation Results\n\n- SPARQL QC checks: **0 violations** (all 16 query rules passed)\n- ELK reasoning: **no unsatisfiable classes, no errors**\n- OBO format conversion: **successful**\n\n### Checklist\n\n- [x] PLAN: Issue analyzed and intent is clear\n- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Ontology validated before any changes (passing)\n- [x] RESEARCH: PMID references validated via PubMed\n- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Relevant terms located (GO:0140177, GO:7770062)\n- [x] EDITS: Correct checkin/checkout procedure followed for GO:0140177\n- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: GO:7770062 appropriately placed under GO:0140177\n- [x] METADATA: term_tracker_item added for tracked definition change\n- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: SPARQL-QC and ELK reasoning pass after edit\n- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: go-edit.obo committed with detailed message\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778899820997,"end":1778899821005}},"id":"prt_e2eb10dc8001WTTIAy93LuVoAo","sessionID":"ses_1d1560b64ffene3xA8b0eZNPB1","messageID":"msg_e2eb0fb3b001Z4nfGTxs8OJ3H2"}}
